{{Advert|date=October 2017}}
There are a variety of dates that have been designated as '''"Chocolate Day"''' around the world. The most commonly accepted such date is '''July 7.'''{{Citation needed|date=October 2017}} Various Chocolate Days have been called Local, National or [[World Chocolate Day|International/World]], including conflicting claims.{{Citation needed|date=October 2017}}
The U.S. National Confectioners Association lists four primary chocolate holidays on their calendar<ref name="candyusa.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.candyusa.com/life-candy/candy-holidays/|title=Candy Holidays|work=National Confectioners Association|accessdate=2 October 2017}}</ref>{{Synthesis inline|date=October 2017}} (Chocolate Day (July 7), two National Chocolate Days (October 28 and December 28), and International Chocolate Day (September 13)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.candyusa.com/news/reasons-to-celebrate-candy-in-september/|title=Reasons to celebrate chocolate in September|work=National Confectioners Association|accessdate=2 October 2017}}</ref>), in addition to variants such as National Milk Chocolate Day, National White Chocolate Day, and National Cocoa Day.
International Chocolate Day coincides with the birth date of [[Milton S. Hershey]] (September 13, 1857),<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.biography.com/people/milton-hershey-9337133 | title=Milton Hershey Biography | publisher=[[Biography.com]] | accessdate=2 October 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Creative Forecasting|volume=20|issue=7-12|page=6|title="September 2008 dates to celebrate"|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7JPgAAAAMAAJ&q=International+Chocolate+Day+-+This+day+celebrates+the+birth+anniversary+of+Milton+Hershey |accessdate=7 July 2014|quote=International Chocolate Day - This day celebrates the birth anniversary of Milton Hershey (1857 - 1945)}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thehersheycompany.com/en_us/news-center/blog/milton-hershey-happy-birthday-to-the-man-who-gave-us-inspiration-and-innovation.html | title=Milton Hershey: Happy Birthday | publisher=The Hershey Company | accessdate=2 October 2017}}</ref> founder of [[The Hershey Company|The Hershey Chocolate Company]].
