'''''Rikki and Me''''' was a stage show celebrating the life of comic actor [[Rikki Fulton]], it starred [[Gerard Kelly]] and [[Tony Roper (actor)|Tony Roper]] as [[Jack Milroy]] and [[Rikki Fulton]].<ref>{{cite web|author= |url=https://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/rikki-s-comedy-legend-lives-on-1-1001165 |title=Rikki's comedy legend lives on |publisher=The Scotsman |date=2006-10-10 |accessdate=2018-11-03}}</ref> The show was a huge success all over theatres in [[Scotland]] and is now available on DVD.

